      "body" : "I don't _generally_ like the idea of the validator \"fixing\" broken addresses, because it's perfectly possible for one character variations to also be valid.  ... but the case of random entities stuffed in, that seems pretty safe to fix to me.  Perhaps we should decode any entities, then strip only whitespace/linebreaks?",
